units si
atom_style granular
atom_modify map array
atom_modify sort 0 0.0
boundary f f f
newton off
communicate mode single vel yes
hard_particles yes
soft_particles yes

region reg block -0.0012 0.0012 -0.0012 0.0012 -0.0012 0.0012 units box
create_box 1 reg
neighbor 1.0e-4 bin
neigh_modify delay 0

fix m1 all property/global youngsModulus peratomtype 9.0e10
fix m2 all property/global poissonsRatio peratomtype 0.25
fix m3 all property/global coefficientRestitution peratomtypepair 1 0.3
fix m4 all property/global coefficientFriction peratomtypepair 1 0.5
fix b1 all property/global radiusMultiplierBond peratomtypepair 1 1.0
fix b2 all property/global normalBondStiffnessPerUnitArea peratomtypepair 1 1.0e14
fix b3 all property/global tangentialBondStiffnessPerUnitArea peratomtypepair 1 5.0e13
fix b4 all property/global maxSigmaBond peratomtypepair 1 5.0e7
fix b5 all property/global maxTauBond peratomtypepair 1 5.0e7
fix b6 all property/global dampingNormalForceBond peratomtypepair 1 0.0
fix b7 all property/global dampingTangentialForceBond peratomtypepair 1 0.0
fix b8 all property/global dampingNormalTorqueBond peratomtypepair 1 0.0
fix b9 all property/global dampingTangentialTorqueBond peratomtypepair 1 0.0
fix b10 all property/global tsCreateBond scalar 1.0
fix b11 all property/global createDistanceBond peratomtypepair 1 2.0e-4

pair_style gran model hertz tangential history cohesion bond stressBreak on createBondAlways off
pair_coeff * *

fix mesh_bottom all mesh/surface/stress file ../meshes/bottom_plate.stl type 1
fix mesh_top all mesh/surface/stress file ../meshes/top_plate.stl type 1
fix wall_all all wall/gran model hertz tangential history cohesion bond mesh n_meshes 2 meshes mesh_bottom mesh_top stressBreak on createBondAlways off

run 0
